    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Educational institutions devoted to the professional study of the organization and management of commercial enterprises, usually at the baccalaureate level and above. For buildings that house schools devoted to training students in the clerical aspects of business and commerce, use "business colleges."</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
